__section__
default
__description__
Bitpay button to subscribe to this site.

* user
* constants
	bitpay_image_src		location of the bitpay button image

	
* gift	hashref passed if handling a gift subscription.  Should contain values
        for keys uid, and puid (uid of user receiving subscription, uid of purchaser)

* from  string user wants included in e-mail message 

__title__

__page__
subscribe
__lang__
en_US
__name__
bitpaybut
__template__
<form method="POST" action="/bitpay.pl">
<input type="hidden" name="from" value="[% from %]">
<input type="hidden" name="uid" value="[% uid %]">
<input type="hidden" name="puid" value="[% puid %]">
<input type="hidden" name="amount" value="[% amount %]">
<input type="hidden" name="days" value="[% days %]">
<input type="image" src="[% constants.bitpay_image_src %]" name="submit" alt="Subscribe With Bitpay">
</form>
